  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This randomized controlled study was designed to evaluate the accuracy, safety and clinical
      outcomes of the robot assisted spinal surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Robot assisted operation is new for spinal surgery, in this study, we will evaluate the
      accuracy, safety and clinical outcomes compared with traditional free hand operation.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
